===2015=== '''FSGP 2015''' was held again at [[Circuit of the Americas]] on July 29–31. It was won by [[Iowa State University]] with 223 total laps and a fast lap of 4:30.444, both track records for solar cars. <ref>[http://americansolarchallenge.org/the-competition/fsgp-2015/ FSGP 2015 page]</ref> Hot weather forced most of the teams to have to pull into the pits at times to cool their batteries. The [[University of Calgary]] became the first Cruiser team to compete in FSGP.
